hopobject.body: How much does the job pay? kenby pharmacy "And you were only 22," says Sir Tim. "Not that you can't do it at 22." Well quite. Another composer was a mere teenager when Rice first fruitfully collaborated with him on Joseph and the Amazing Technicolor Dreamcoat. By coincidence Andrew Lloyd Webber happens to have a new show opening in the same West End season. Stephen Ward, based on the Profumo affair, is written with his Sunset Boulevard collaborators Christopher Hampton and Don Black.
